OL,3,CGovernment will 'consider' scrapping
OL,4,Ctwo-child benefit cap, minister says
OL,6,FThe government will consider scrapping
OL,7,Fthe controversial two-child benefit
OL,8,Fcap, a cabinet minister has said amid
OL,9,Fgrowing pressure for the measure to be
OL,10,Fdropped.
OL,12,FEducation Secretary Bridget Phillipson
OL,13,Fsaid scrapping the cap would be looked
OL,14,Fat "as one of a number of ways" to
OL,15,Flift children out of poverty,
OL,16,Fsignalling a softening of the
OL,17,Fgovernment's previous position and
OL,18,Fpaving the way for a potential U-turn.
