OL,3,CGovernment will 'consider' scrapping
OL,4,Ctwo-child benefit cap, minister says
OL,6,FIt comes as Sir Keir Starmer could
OL,7,Fface the threat of his first backbench
OL,8,Frevolt over the benefit cap that
OL,9,Faffects some 1.6 million children.
OL,11,FThe PM has been urged by charities,
OL,12,Fopposition parties and some of his own
OL,13,FMPs to abolish the limit, as child
OL,14,Fpoverty rates rise.
OL,16,FThe SNP has tabled an amendment to the
OL,17,FKing's Speech calling for the cap to
OL,18,Fbe axed and left-wing Labour MPs are
OL,19,Fexpected to weigh in further to a
OL,20,Fdebate, which could happen on Monday
OL,21,Fafternoon.
