OL,4,Ctwo-child benefit cap, minister says
OL,6,FMs Phillipson said the possible
OL,7,Fscrapping of the limit would be looked
OL,8,Fat by a new taskforce she is leading
OL,9,Fwith Work and Pensions Secretary Liz
OL,10,FKendall as part of a review of
OL,11,Fpotential policies to reduce child
OL,12,Fpoverty.
OL,14,FSpeaking to ITV News, she said the
OL,15,Fgovernment "will look at all the
OL,16,Flevers" causing child poverty.
