OL,3,CGovernment will 'consider' scrapping
OL,4,Ctwo-child benefit cap, minister says
OL,6,FIn an interview with Sky News, Ms
OL,7,FPhillipson went further on:
OL,8,F"Unfortunately, it's also a very
OL,9,Fexpensive measure, but we will need to
OL,10,Fconsider it as one of a number of
OL,11,Flevers in terms of how we make sure we
OL,12,Flift children out of poverty."
OL,14,FIn a speech at the Farnborough
OL,15,FInternational Airshow, Starmer was
OL,16,Fasked about the pressure to scrap the
OL,17,Ftwo-child limit, saying "it's good
OL,18,Fwe're having a debate about it."
